QuestData.Title: Goods from Silvermoon City
QuestData.Description: Welcome volunteer! We're running low on supplies here, but Silvermoon has promised us materiel assistance. That's where you come in.$B$BTake this list over to Skymaster Brightdawn. He'll have further instructions for you on how best to get up to Silvermoon City.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver Sathiel's Request to Skymaster Brightdawn in Fairbreeze Village.
QuestData.RewardText: Sathiel wants you to head up to Silvermoon City and bring back her goods, huh? Sure, I can get you there quickly... for a small fee, of course.
